{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_50","type":"agent_message","text":"The important comparison result is that a nearby Liquibase version (`4.27.0` metadata on the `4.25.0` fixture) also crashes the traced launcher in the same way. That means the failure mode is tied to the Liquibase metadata/test setup under tracing, not a one-off bad entry introduced only in `5.0.1`. I’m now testing whether the crash disappears when the Liquibase repo metadata is excluded, which will tell me if we’re dealing with a specific repo metadata block versus the library/test fixture itself."}}
